ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2009-10
PrecisAppointment of PHILIPPE BEAULNE as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Moldova, with residence in Bucharest; ARIEL DELOUYA as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Tunisia; JAMES FOX as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of San Marino, with residence in Rome; PIERRE GUIMOND as Ambassador of Canada to Bosnia-Herzegovina, with residence in Budapest; RON HOFFMANN as Ambassador of Canada to the Lao People's Democratic Republic, with residence in Bangkok; DENIS KINGSLEY as Ambassador of Canada to the Federal Republic of Nigeria; STEPHEN MILLAR as Ambassador of Canada to the Kyrgyz Republic, with residence in Almaty; ROBERTA SANTI as Ambassador of Canada to the Swiss Confederation, with concurrent accreditation to the Principality of Liechtenstein; and GRAHAM SHANTZ as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Spain, with concurrent accreditation to the Principality of Andorra.
